                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Find the next smaller and next larger integers with the same number of 1 bits. This maps to LCCI 5.4. Typical interview angle: For next larger: find rightmost \"01\" pattern and swap to \"10\". For next smaller: find rightmost \"10\" pattern and swap to \"01\". Edge cases: all-1 bit sequences and numbers like powers of 2."
